title: President of Turkmenistan arrives in Tashkent (Government of the Republic of Uzbekistan)
text: ( Source : Government of the Republic of Uzbekistan ) At the invitation of the President of Uzbekistan Islam Karimov on October 7, 2015 , the President of Turkmenistan paid an official visit to Tashkent . At the Tashkent International Airport
